dct_title_s: Russia in Europe, Sweden, and Norway
dct_description_sm: Cartographic Details: Scale [1:15,840,000] Relief shown by hachures; depth shown by isolines. Shows provinces, rivers, railroads, cities and towns. Inset maps show Denmark, Holland, and Belguim. From: Mitchell's new general atlas. Philadelphia : S. Augustus Mitchell, 1860.
1 map : color ; 34 x 27 centimeters, on sheet 39 x 32 centimeters
